Hey, Big Bird... Little Sparrow... Bird Brain or what ever your new Indian handle is, I have GREAT NEWS!<br><br>
Research and Development just called and promised to have the Dock Spatz Doll ready by Christmas (Jesus will be pleased!)<br><br>
The laboratory guys report that after winding up and releasing the prototype it functioned and then malfunctioned (consistent with the original concept.)  It blurted out contradictory messages, insulted and patronized, spewed profanities at the little G.I. Joe doll (not included in the purchase price of 5 rubles) and immediately hid under the couch.<br><br>
NOTE:  We are having a problem getting both left footed sandels off sync.<br><br>
Get back to me soon, Field Rat Breath, I have a proposal for a companion doll which may go over big in Russia, China and Canada.  We may call it &quot;The Disappearing Dick Doll!&quot;  Come on, Cetan... work with me.<br><br>
